  "body": "当slider轮播内容大于2个时可以一直往左/右滑动，滑到底后仍然可以循环滑动。但是当slide内容只有两个时，滑动到最后一个部就不能再继续滑动了，得反方向滑动。\r\n\r\n我是在android上复现的,下面是demo代码：\r\n```html\r\n<style>\r\n  .wrapper {\r\n    background-color:#00ff00;\r\n  }\r\n  .slider {\r\n    width: 750;\r\n    height: 100;\r\n  }\r\n  .row-items {\r\n    width: 750;\r\n    height: 100;\r\n    margin:10;\r\n    background-color:#ff0000;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<template>\r\n    <div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n      <slider class=\"slider\" auto-play=\"false\">\r\n        <div class=\"row-items\" repeat=\"{{row in dataShops}}\">\r\n          <text style=\"font-size:100;\">{{row}}</text>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </slider>\r\n   </div>\r\n</template>\r\n\r\n<script>\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  data: {\r\n    dataShops:[1,2] // 改成[1,2,3,4]就可以无限滑动了\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n期望2个也能无限滑动。\r\n"
